   Yaratguvchim Qutqaruvchim
.                Am                 D      G
   Chin yurakdan mening Rabbimni olqishlayman
.                 Am7  D          G     Em
   Mening quvvatim mening hayotim Rabbim
.      Am7     D7          G C G
   Iso Masihni olqishlayman</lyrics>
<title>Chin yurakdan</title>
</song>